A third year bachelor student of journalism and communication who has specialized on communication acquires during at least three-week-long practical training his/her first experience of working as a communication assistant, becomes acquainted with communication management of one organization, practices applying elementary communication analysis methods, practices analysis based solving of communication problems and reflects his/her professional development.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The objective of the practical training is: * acquire first experience of communication management assistant profession in safe environment * become better acquainted with communication management of one organization * apply elementary communication analysis methods * practice analysis based solving of communication problems * learn to reflect own professional developmentLearning outcomes/õpiväljund:  When a student has completed the course successfully, he/she: * has first experience of working as a communication assistant * has practiced analysing communication management of one organization * can apply elementary communication analysis methods * has practiced analysis based solving of communication problems * knows how to reflect own professional development
